gov.nasa.worldwind.util.webview
Class BasicWebViewFactory

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.worldwind.util.webview.BasicWebViewFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
WebViewFactory
public class BasicWebViewFactory
extends Object
implements WebViewFactory

Factory implementation for creating WebView instances. This implementation detected the operating system, and creates an instance of WebView appropriate for that system. On Windows, it creates WindowsWebView. On Mac OS, it creates MacWebView. Other operating systems are not supported at this time.
